<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied></hi> cupāṉu varu<hi rend="grantha">ṣa</hi>m tai mātam cakāttam <num value="1386"><g type="numeral">1000</g> 3 <g type="numeral">100</g> 8 <g type="numeral">10</g> 6</num> mel cellāniṉ
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṟa muḻutakuṭi Uṭaiyāṉ Aracaṉāṉa vallāḷatevar paṇṇivitta nāya
<lb n="3" break="no"/>kar tiruaraṅkum maṇṭapamum tiruppaṇi kaḷantai nāyakar A<unclear>m</unclear>mu
<lb n="4" break="no"/>tu ceyyumpaṭikku Ivvūr vayalil Eṉ kāṇi Āṉa taṉmam Eṉkiṟa cey
<lb n="5"/>taṭi 3 l nilam (1/4) Ituvum melaitteruvil maṉai 1 kku kol 3m ca<hi rend="grantha">ndrā</hi>tittiyavaraiyum
<lb n="6"/>tirunāmattukkāṇi Āka Aṉupavittukkoḷḷavum §
